c: 3
v: 52
t: "(Having preached his message in this way for a long time) Jesus perceived their willful persistence on unbelief (and open hostility), and called out: \"Who will be my helpers (on this way) to God?\" The disciples answered: \"We are the helpers of God(’s cause). We believe in God, and (we call you to) bear witness that we are Muslims (submitted to Him exclusively)"